**color in tailwind**

1-Blue background and white text
`<div class="bg-blue-500 text-white p-4">`
`hi`
`</div>`

2-When you pass the item the color changes
`<div class="bg-green-400 hover:bg-green-600 text-white p-4">`
  `start`
`</div>`


**note:**
bg-<color>-<number> → background color
text-<color>-<number> → text color
border-<color>-<number> → color of the border
